caption: Ordered through grub hub about 45 minutes prior to closing. Said the order was received and they were making it. About 40 minutes later received a text saying the order was cancelled and they were closed. That's all, no other explanation. Food is good, but will not order from them again.

Saw this place listed on uberEATS. Ordered a couple sandwiches. 15 minutes later they canceled the order, no explanation given. I tried calling them, phone rings off the hook then finally a "this person is not available" message. If you're going to be on uberEATS, actually complete your orders. I won't be giving them another try.
Food is consistently delicious.  Be sure to ask for the free sandwich club card.  Seven hits gets a free one.
Sandwiches were good. But Jimmy and his customer service is lacking. "Yeah I messed up the sandwich. What do you want me to do about it?" Well I guess nothing. Will not spend money here again.
